TERMS OF DISTRIBUTION

These reference assemblies are hosted and distributed publicly by the monksilly team with explicit permission from Dark Machine Games. This data is provided solely to facilitate community mod development for White Knuckle.

USAGE RESTRICTIONS

In alignment with the permission granted by the developers, these files are strictly for the creation of good-natured mods. They may not be used to create:
- Trainers
- Cheats, hacks, or exploits
- Malicious tools altering game integrity

If you wish to use or distribute these files outside of the scope of White Knuckle modding, you must obtain your own independent permission from Dark Machine Games.